data.description: Welcome to 43598 Bow Canyon Road, a beautiful newly renovated mountain oasis in the heart of the highly sought after Moonridge neighborhood in Big Bear Lake, California. This property is the home of your dreams! Convenient to skiing, hiking, golfing, and more! In 2020 the home was completely renovated and boasts an open concept floor plan, beautiful glass stair case wrap around deck, beautiful state of the art kitchen and more. From the location to the high end finishes this cabin is guaranteed to check all your boxes. The pplit floorpan consists of two bedrooms, laundry, and full bathroom on the main floor with kitchen, living room, and 3/4 bath upstairs. This mountain beauty comes fully furnished and features must haves like a Vitamix blender, hot tub, and more! Currently the home is designed to sleep 8; the spacious master features a queen size bed, two sets of twin over full bunks in the second bedroom, and a pullout sofa in the living room. This mountain retreat has everything you need to make this your next home or rental property: all this home needs is you!    Seller is a licensed real estate agent.
